Summary: Describes the `pseudolocalization_enabled` property of TranslationServer.

pseudolocalization_enabled (bool): If `true`, enables the use of pseudolocalization on the main translation domain. See ProjectSettings.internationalization/pseudolocalization/use_pseudolocalization for details. Default: false.
